92965df1154352ac5c7fbe","tid":457456,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T17:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyWsYHc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyWsYHc.png&h=03083cb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9243b2a1920b7d06526e1826332b061003030b2e","tid":457456,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T17:18:10.000Z","msg":"推到多啲人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fdda06b2c04a5934a4504746abf5ca7d2fbabb","tid":457456,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"174b4b6e2a5d1bb84ade7bdabce4f691aa118eb3","tid":457456,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77086c897dc492d51642f2647481873d02cbe3a9","tid":457456,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T03:45:54.000Z","msg":"除了由北洋政府帶動的華工團，香港市民在一戰亦有犧牲，有洋人參軍作戰（如皇仁師生），亦有華人投身後勤。<br />\n<br />\n浸大歷史系助理教授鄺智文曾在著作中指出，1916年印度陸軍後勤工程隊與皇家工兵曾在香港招募華工，並把他們送往米索不達米亞前線以擊敗鄂圖曼帝國，負責工程及運輸等後勤工作，戰爭期間共有384名香港華工在伊拉克陣亡。<br />\n<br />\n以虞美人花悼念一戰陣亡軍人是源自英詩《在法蘭德斯戰場》（In Flanders Fields）。當年軍醫麥克雷（John McCrae）目睹戰友之死，把戰場上綻放的鮮紅虞美人花海寫入詩。1921年，英國退伍軍人組織提議義賣虞美人紙花籌款，幫助戰中殉職、傷殘或受戰爭影響的軍人及其家人。"},{"pid":"deaca185ed0dcc5eac1ee8f164b501991dddb3ec","tid":457456,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/257557/11%E6%9C%8811%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A2%E5%85%89%E6%A3%8D%E7%AF%80-%E4%B8%80%E6%88%B0%E5%81%9C%E6%88%B0100%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E8%88%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%95%E9%97%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F257557%2F11%25E6%259C%258811%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%2